title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh, Hello - Recess
description:
"Oh Hello" with Recess talks about the band relocating from Texas to Brooklyn, the meaning of their name and working within the unique atmosphere of the Converse Rubber Tracks studio.
For more information on Rubber Tracks visit:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
